Package org.example.model.warehouse

Class WeatherFact

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.example.model.warehouse.WeatherFact
  • public class WeatherFact
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a fact table for storing weather-related data in a data warehouse. This class is used to store measured weather data, associating it with datetime and location dimensions.
